ActDepartment of Citizenship and Immigration Act
SubjectAtlantic Immigration Pilot Program ** Agreement **
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Citizenship and Immigration, pursuant to subsections 5(1) of the Department of Citizenship and Immigration Act and 8(1) of the Immigration and Refugee Protection Act, to enter into the CANADA-NOVA SCOTIA AGREEMENT, the CANADA-NEW BRUNSWICK AGREEMENT, the CANADA-PRINCE EDWARD ISLAND AGREEMENT, and the CANADA-NEWFOUNDLAND AND LABRADOR AGREEMENT on the Atlantic Immigration Pilot Program, with the Governments of Nova Scotia, New Brunswick, Prince Edward Island, and Newfoundland and Labrador, respectively. The effective period of the Agreements begins upon the date the Agreements are signed by the respective parties and ends on December 31, 2019.
